{"lemma":"خُرْقُ","slug":"خُرْقُ","root":"خ.ر.ق","root_slug":"خ-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خُرْقُ","root":"خرق","pos":"V","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10430","n10431","n10432","n10433","n10434","n10435","n10440"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"unskilled, someone who has no skill or profession"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"stupid, clumsy, incompetent"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Color or defect adjective from the root خ ر ق (ḵ r q).\n\nSee the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":["/ʔax.raq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10430","headword_ar":"خَرْقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", originally an inf. n., of 1: (S, Mgh, Msb, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perforation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, KL,) in a garment, (S, TA,) and in a wall, (Msb, TA,) &c.: (Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a round hole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perforation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the ear of a sheep: (S, Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuruwqN","text_ar":"خُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Mgh, Msb.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~asaEa Alxaroqu EalaY Alr~aAqiEi","text_ar":"اِتَّسَعَ الخَرْقُ عَلَى الرَّاقِعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The hole was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, wide to the patcher"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A part that has a hole made in it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is rent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"torn, of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from, a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A desert;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoraqN","text_ar":"مَخْرَقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a desert far extending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA,) whether"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"level"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not level:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓ the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wide desert in which the winds"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blow irregularly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and the former, (El-Muärrij, K,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaroqaA='N","text_ar":"خَرْقَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) signifies likewise"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wide land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wide country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Muärrij,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the winds"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blow irregularly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Muärrij, K: [see 7:]) ISh says, the space between El-Basrah and Hafr Abee-Moosà is a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaroq","text_ar":"خَرْق"},{"kind":"text","text":", and that between En-Nibáj and Dareeyeh is a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaroq","text_ar":"خَرْق"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuruwqN","text_ar":"خُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawoqaA='u","text_ar":"خَوْقَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafaAzapN xaroqaA='u","text_ar":"مَفَازَةٌ خَرْقَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A farextending desert."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTaEonaA A_ilayokumo A^aroDFA","text_ar":"قَطَعْنَا اـِلَيْكُمْ اَرْضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaroqaA='a","text_ar":"خَرْقَا=ءَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaruwqFA","text_ar":"خَرُوقًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We have traversed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in journeying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to you, a wide land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wide land in which the winds blow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain plant, resembling the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qusoT","text_ar":"قُسْط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (JK, Ibn-'Abbád, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having leaves."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Ibn- 'Abbád.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","TA","KL","K","JK"]},{"entry_id":"n10431","headword_ar":"خُرْقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xariqa","text_ar":"خَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) [or perhaps inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaruqa","text_ar":"خَرُقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xariqa","text_ar":"خَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (see 1, last two sentences,)] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuruqN","text_ar":"خُرُقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Roughness, ungentleness, clumsiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"awkwardness; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rifoqN","text_ar":"رِفْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (JK, S, * Mgh, Msb, * K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in doing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making, a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unskilfulness in work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the management of affairs: foolishness; stupidity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsoundness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deficiency, in intellect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understanding;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuroqapN","text_ar":"خُرْقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignorance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawomapu Alxuroqi","text_ar":"نَوْمَةُ الخُرْقِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sleep of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the time of morning called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DuHaY","text_ar":"ضُحَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Har p. 223. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HumoqN","text_ar":"حُمْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluqN","text_ar":"خُلُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A2-  The first of these words is also pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoraqu","text_ar":"اَخْرَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and of [its fem.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaroqaA='u","text_ar":"خَرْقَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A3-  Also The she-camel's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vulva."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","TA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n10432","headword_ar":"خِرْقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xir~iyqN","text_ar":"خِرِّيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Liberal, bountiful, munificent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generous;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mixoraAqN","text_ar":"مِخْرَاقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, K:) or ↓ the second signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very liberal"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bountiful"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (K: [so in a later part of the art.:]) or this and the first signify one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who takes a wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an ample, range,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is profuse, in liberality"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bounty"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (TA:) or a youth, or young man, (JK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegant, in mind, manners, address, speech, person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clever,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ingenious; with liberality, bounty, munificence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generosity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, JK, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and courage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, JK:) and a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goodly"},{"kind":"text","text":"youth or young man, [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfatiY~u","text_ar":"الفَتِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the CK, I read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfataY","text_ar":"الفَتَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in other copies of the K,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of generous disposition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) the pl. (of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiroqN","text_ar":"خِرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoraAqN","text_ar":"اَخْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc.] (K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuraAqN","text_ar":"خُرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xur~aAqN","text_ar":"خُرَّاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (accord. to different copies of the K, [both anomalous, and perhaps it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiraAqN","text_ar":"خِرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", agreeably with analogy,]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuruwqN","text_ar":"خُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xir~iyqN","text_ar":"خِرِّيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xir~iyquwna","text_ar":"خِرِّيقُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; no broken pl. of it having been heard. (T, TA.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkaf~i biAln~awaAli","text_ar":"الكَفِّ بِالنَّوَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa mataxar~iqu","text_ar":"هُوَ مَتَخَرِّقُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has a liberal hand, largely beneficent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alk~f~i biAln~awaAli","text_ar":"الكّفِّ بِالنَّوَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa maxoruwqu","text_ar":"هُوَ مَخْرُوقُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is liberal, bountiful, munificent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [But see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoruwqN","text_ar":"مَخْرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.]) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiroqN","text_ar":"خِرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also applied to a spear, meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Highly esteemed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prized; excellent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rare."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["IAar","K","TA","JK","Lth"]},{"entry_id":"n10433","headword_ar":"خَرُقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoraqu","text_ar":"اَخْرَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10434","headword_ar":"خَرِقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xariqa","text_ar":"خَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.:] A young gazelle"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak in the legs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cleaving to the ground, and not rising:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) a gazelle, or young gazelle, (K, TA,) when hunted, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frightened, so as to be unable"},{"kind":"text","text":"to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and in like manner a bird (K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frightened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"page_break","n":729},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impatient,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to be unable to fly away:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And [hence,] A man (Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confounded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perplexed, and unable to see his right course;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bereft of his reason"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intellect, by reason of fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of shame:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confounded, perplexed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amazed, opening his eyes, and looking."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoraqu","text_ar":"اَخْرَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ashes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"because they remain [cleaving to the ground] while the people thereof go away. (K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","Msb","S"]},{"entry_id":"n10435","headword_ar":"خُرُقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuroqN","text_ar":"خُرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10440","headword_ar":"خُرَّقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain bird,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, IDrd, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smaller than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qunobur","text_ar":"قُنْبُر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lark"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (JK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that cleaves to the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of sparrow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so says AHát, in the “ Book of Birds: ” (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAriqu","text_ar":"خَرَارِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (JK, IDrd, K.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","IDrd","K","TA"]}]}}